Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, open the hatch! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:20.59,Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(797.773,777.5)}{\fs55}EPISODE SIX\N{\fs70}DECISIVE BATTLE,\NNEW TOKYO-3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:27.89,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(955.909,785.25)}1/1 Scale Balloon Dummy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's particle beam cannon has hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The dummy has been vaporized!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.91,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(955.909,785.25)}Automated Model 12 Self-Propelled Mortar
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Model 12 Self-Propelled Mortar\Nhas been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,From the data we've collected,\Nwe're assuming that the target
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically attacks any opponent\Nwithin a certain range.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The likelihood of it hitting anything entering\Nthe area with its particle beam is 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:08.93,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,Department of Operations, Nerv Headquarters\NAnalysis Room 2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too risky for close range combat\Nin an Eva, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What about its AT field?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still active.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:22.03,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\pos(1473.591,837)}{\pos(1481.591,837)\c&H05002A&}REPLAY IMAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strong enough that the spatial changes\Nin phase are visible to the naked eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Using half-measures like guided missiles,\Nartillery, or bombs
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,will inflict more damage on us\Nthan on the Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Offensively and defensively it's\Nalmost perfect. A flying fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the status on its drill?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,At this moment the target\Nis directly above us,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,penetrating the New Tokyo-3 Null Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A giant shielded drill with\Na diameter of 17.5 meters
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is boring towards Nerv HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is planning to attack Nerv\NHeadquarters directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sassy bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's its ETA?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:59.94,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs50\c&H010101&\pos(1092.227,237.25)}Japan Standard Time\NRemaining Estimated Time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,12:06:54 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,By that time, it will have breached\Nall twenty-two levels of armor,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:06.86,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HC7F6B2&\pos(1487.773,796.25)}{\pos(1489.773,796.25)}APPROXIMATED\NGRAPHICS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and arrive at Nerv Headquarters itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Less than ten hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:17.58,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs54\c&H03030A&\pos(1465.591,837)}PRESENT TIME
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The drill has contacted the first armor plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the condition of Unit 01?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The defensive armor was melted\Ndown to the third layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:23.38,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,Cage 7, Nerv Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The silver lining is that the central\Ncontrol unit sustained no damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Three more seconds, and\Nit would have been over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In three hours, the replacement parts\Nshould be installed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the status of Unit 00?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Re-activation itself should\Nprove no problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's still a feedback error.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So actual combat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...is still impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the condition of Unit 01's pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:51.99,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,Emergency Room, Central Hospital,\NNerv Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No physical damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,However, his nerve pulses are up by 0.8.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Still within acceptable limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy drill arrival: 9 hours, 55 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation certainly isn't favorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we just raise a white flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we resort to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there's one little thing I'd like to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a sniper to shoot the target\Nfrom outside its firing zone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:17.52,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,Nerv Commander's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of trying to neutralize\Nthe target's AT field,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe a pinpoint shot with a\Nhigh-energy beam is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do the Magi say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The responses from the Magi\NSuper Computers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,were two affirmative and\None conditional affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, our probability of success is 8.7 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite a high percentage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see no reason to raise an objection.\NYou may proceed, Captain Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But you sure have come up with\Na reckless plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Operations Director Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be rude. It's not reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be executed within the\Nnine hours we have left,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and has the highest chance of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing does? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:58.64,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,Eva Positron Rifle\N{\fs45}(Prototype 20 with Toroidal Accelerator)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But our positron rifle can't handle\Nsuch a high output.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll borrow one, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Borrow one? You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! The Strategic SDF Lab's prototype!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.07,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}{\b0\fs80}{\pos(955.909,490.5)\c&H151F22&}Requisition Order
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nerv is hereby requisitioning this\NSelf Propelled Positron Cannon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.79,0:07:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,as of 15:00 today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:21.87,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60}Tsukuba Technology Laboratory Headquarters, Strategic SDF
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, this is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:24.84,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,Special Units Hangar 4
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll try to return this in as close\Nto its original condition as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We appreciate your cooperation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Rei! Take it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a piece of precision machinery,\Nso be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, our calculations\Nshow that it will take
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,at least 180 million kilowatts to\Npenetrate that AT field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going to get\Nthat much electricity?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Where else? From all of Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:01.66,Signs,,0,0,0,,Giant Power Outage Today All Across Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We apologize for interrupting
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,our regular programming for this\NEmergency Bulletin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,Suzuhara Residence
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,From 11:30 PM tonight\Nuntil tomorrow morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.33,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,Horaki Residence
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:07.84,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,New Tokyo-2
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be a large scale power blackout
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout most of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:11.34,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,New Makurazaki, Kagoshima Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We appreciate your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeat, from 11:30 PM tonight\Nuntil tomorrow morning
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:17.81,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(695.091,214.7)}{\pos(951.091,134.7)\c&HEAFFFF&}At dawn today,\Na large-scale\N power outage\Nall across the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.72,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(972.8,776.6)}Betsukai, Hokkaido
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.52,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,Ube, Yamaguchi Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be a large scale power\Nblackout throughout Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We appreciate your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:25.27,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,Mitaka Ward, Old Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.77,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,New Tokyo-3
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:31.94,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,579.8)}Control Room, General Operations\NCommand Center, Nerv Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The drill has just broken through\Nthe seventh defensive layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the status on our energy system?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:36.37,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,New Odawara, Kanagawa Prefecture
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,3.2% behind schedule, but we should\Nmanage to be finished by 23:10.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And the positron rifle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,On the honor of Technology\NDevelopment Department 3,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:45.79,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}Technology Department Division 3, Nerv Headquarters\N{\fs45}(In charge of electromagnetic and light wave hardware)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll have it built for you in three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What about our defensive measures?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, using a shield is about all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:51.46,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,Hangar 8, Nerv Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:55.59,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs55}Eva Anti-Heat and Light Wave Defensive Equipment\N{\fs45}(Makeshift Specs)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is the shield?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's a hand-me-down from\Na single stage to orbit rocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:09:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It may look ugly, but it's got a super-\Nelectromagnetic base coating that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Section 2 guarantees will stand up to\Nthe enemy's particle beam
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,for at least seventeen seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Have you determined\Nthe sniper position?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the range to the target,\Ngeographical features,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and taking power access into consideration,\Nthis would be the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The sniping position will be atop Mt. Futago!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The operation will commence\Nat 00:00 tomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,From this point on, this operation will be\Ncalled "Operation Yashima".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the only remaining problem\Nis the pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01's designated pilot is conscious now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:49.77,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,Cage 7 Control Room
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,His examination results look normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Then, the operation will\Nproceed as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder if he'll pilot it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready for a decisive battle at Mt. Futago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:04.16,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,Surgical Ward 3, Central Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to brief you on the timetable\Nof Operation Yashima,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,which will begin tomorrow at 00:00 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Pilots Ikari and Ayanami will arrive\Nat the cage at 17:30 today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,At 18:00, Units 01 and 00 will activate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch is at 18:05.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They will arrive at the temporary base\Non Mt. Futago at 18:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There, they will stand by and\Nawait further orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The operation will begin\Npromptly at midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't show up half-asleep looking like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All I've been doing since\Nyesterday is apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to eat anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be departing in sixty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have to pilot that thing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.63,0:11:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can be so cool about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because you haven't had the kind\Nof experiences I've had yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go through that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you stay in bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay in bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pilot Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Akagi is already prepared to rewrite\NUnit 01's personal data files.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Ritsuko is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving. Captain Katsuragi and\NDr. Akagi will be waiting at the cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:28.01,Fancy Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,221.6)}{\fs80}No School Today
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:28.01,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H101C35&\pos(960,752.6)}New Tokyo-3 Public Middle School 1 Principal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're awfully late. We oughta\Nevacuate to the shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I hacked into my dad's data files.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this is the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but they still ain't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The mountain is moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Evangelions!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it! We're counting on you!\NEvangelion! Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.26,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,8:11 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:16.60,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,Near Asahi Falls on Mt. Futago
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The drill has penetrated through\Nthe 17th layer of armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It will reach headquarters in\N3 hours 55 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem with the hub\Nsynchronization system.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Power supply transfer from Shikoku\Nand Kyushu is completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin tests of each cooling system.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a piece of precision machinery,\Nso handle it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:38.54,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,Eva Positron Sniper Rifle\N{\fs40}(Nerv Specs - Formerly Strategic SDF Lab's Automated Positron Rifle)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing wasn't built for field operations.\NWill it really work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no choice.\NThis is a makeshift solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So it'll be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Theoretically, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we won't know if the cannon barrel\Nand accelerator will hold until we try firing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time it's been fired\Nwith such a high power output.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are your individual duties\Nfor the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Unit 01 will be the gunner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei, you're in charge of defense with Unit 00.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is because Shinji has a higher\Nsync ratio with Unit 01,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and this operation will require\Nexceptional precision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the positron beam will be\Ninfluenced by the Earth's gravity,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,magnetic fields and rotation,\Nit will not fire in a straight line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You must remember to make\Nadjustments for these deviations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You must penetrate the core precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've never practiced this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do what the manual says.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When the indicators converge\Nin the center, pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The computers will handle the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, once you fire it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it will take time before you can fire again
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for cooling, reloading,\Nand replacement of the fuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, if I miss and the enemy shoots back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think about unnecessary\Nthings right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just think about destroying it in one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's crisis time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to defend Unit 01, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time. Both of you, get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We might die doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.04,Signs,,0,0,0,,...a large-scale power outage all across...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you pilot this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm bound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bound?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,With my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,With all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very strong, Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I have nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "you have nothing else"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The time is now 00:00:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:10.96,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,Type 14 Large Mobile Command Car
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:13.92,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1340.191,58.2)}{\fs70\c&H000003&}Japan Standard Time
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Commencing operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.05,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000A04&\pos(960,759)}Inside Command Car
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, we're entrusting you with\Nall the electricity of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiate primary connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiating power transmission from\Ndistricts number 1 through 803.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 1 transmission system nominal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem with hub synchronizer output.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All transmission induction systems activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Conversion efficiency staying\Nwithin estimated values.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Voltage is rising. Reaching pressure zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All cooling systems, full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Electron condenser system nominal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Auxiliary system activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Temperature stable. No problems detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Positron charge is nominal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiate secondary connection!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All accelerators engaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Activate convergence unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Transmitting all power to Mt. Futago\Ntemporary substation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No problems reported\Nwith tertiary connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Release final safety systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear the chamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:09.98,Signs,,0,0,0,,Safe Empty
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:10.56,Signs,,0,0,0,,Armed\NLoaded
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Error correction for Earth rotation\Nand gravity is plus 0.0009.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Voltage is 0.2 short of critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Seventh and final connection engaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All photo-electron fuses,\Ncommence convergence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Transmitting all energy to the positron rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,8...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,7...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,6...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,5...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,High energy output detected from the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,4...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,3...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,2...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy drill has broken\Ninto the Geo-Front!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire two! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Replacing fuses! Initiating recharge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Barrel cooling in progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Resume positron acceleration!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Another high energy reading\Ncoming from the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The shield won't last!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we ready yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten more seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:19:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say... Don't say that\Nyou have nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say goodbye when you leave\Non a mission. It's too sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.92,0:21:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I don't know what to do\Nat a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:00.46,Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1043.4,687)}TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:06.78,Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(790.4,34.2)}PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The humanoid weapon\Nthat the civilans developed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to fight against the encroaching Angels\Ngoes out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Misato be able to stop the meltdown?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the next episode:\N"That Which is Manmade"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.79,0:23:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:20.92,ED Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,730.2)}THAT WHICH IS MANMADE
